Frontoethmoidal Osteoma with Secondary Intradural Mucocele Extension Causing 
Frontal Lobe Syndrome and Pneumocephalus: Case Report and Review of Literature.

Licci M(1), Zweifel C(1), Hench J(2), Guzman R(1), Soleman J(3).

